- **FIX [2026-03-29]: session-audit.js + Ghost both extracted decisions → duplication** — decisions extraction removed from session-audit.js; Ghost is the owner of decisions lifecycle. <!-- decay:2026-03-29 tier:cold rel:0.565 -->
- **FIX [2026-03-29]: Haiku prompt too permissive → 9 non-system facts extracted** — prompt hardened with system-config-only constraint; `NEVER infer/fabricate` + `empty > wrong`. <!-- decay:2026-03-29 tier:cold rel:0.565 -->
- **FIX [2026-03-29]: trace-collector.db unbounded growth** — added 7-day TTL + `PRAGMA wal_checkpoint(TRUNCATE)` to SQLite maintenance routine. <!-- decay:2026-03-29 tier:cold rel:0.565 -->
- **FIX [2026-03-29]: Pending report disappearing after /compact** — compact-report-injector.js was deleting PENDING block before reading it; fix: save to MEMORY.md, Claude deletes after output. <!-- decay:2026-03-29 tier:cold rel:0.565 -->
- **FIX [2026-03-29]: video-insight-router.js modified vault without commit → auto-pull blocked** — added auto-commit (`git add -A && git commit`) before git pull to avoid rebase conflicts. <!-- decay:2026-03-29 tier:cold rel:0.565 -->
