- **FIX [2026-03-29]: Dataview TABLE FROM does not parse inline fields** — replaced with DataviewJS + regex; include `inCodeBlock` flag to skip lines inside fenced code blocks. <!-- decay:2026-03-29 tier:cold rel:0.565 -->
- **FIX [2026-03-29]: session-audit with Haiku hallucinated facts** — replaced Haiku with claude-sonnet-4-6 for accuracy-critical extraction tasks. <!-- decay:2026-03-29 tier:cold rel:0.565 -->
- **FIX [2026-03-30]: recall=0% on all eval queries → skills evicted from system prompt** — root cause: 15K SLASH_COMMAND_TOOL_CHAR_BUDGET limit too small; fix: increase to 50000 in settings.json. Diagnostic: check budget × number-of-skills × avg-description-size. <!-- decay:2026-03-30 tier:cold rel:0.58 -->
